paragraphs.title: SQOOP CASIM
paragraphs.text:
%sh
kinit -kt jpinelli.keytab jpinelli;
hadoop fs -rm -r /user/jpinelli/camp_terminales_casim_1; --cambiar
sqoop-import --connect 'jdbc:teradata://telearg7/DATABASE=AR_PROD_HUB_DIM_VW,CHARSET=UTF8' --username  --password  --query "
select	 a12.Anio_Mes_NU  mes,
a11.Fecha_Fin_Orden_ID as fecha,
	a16.Tipo_Cliente_DE  tipo_cliente,
	a11.Valor_Recurso_Primario_CD  ani,
	sum(1)  q
from	AR_PROD_HUB_DIM_VW.F_TR_Cambio_SIM_D	a11
	join	AR_PROD_HUB_DIM_VW.D_Calendario	a12
	  on 	(a11.Fecha_Fin_Orden_ID = a12.Fecha_ID)
	join	AR_PROD_HUB_DIM_VW.D_Producto_T3	a13
	  on 	(a11.Producto_T3_ID = a13.Producto_T3_ID)
	join	AR_PROD_HUB_DIM_VW.D_SUB_TIPO_CLIENTE	a14
	  on 	(a11.Sub_Tipo_Cliente_ID = a14.Sub_Tipo_Cliente_ID)
	join	AR_PROD_HUB_DIM_VW.D_Anio_Mes	a15
	  on 	(a12.Anio_Mes_NU = a15.Anio_Mes_ID)
	join	AR_PROD_HUB_DIM_VW.D_TIPO_CLIENTE	a16
	  on 	(a14.Tipo_Cliente_ID = a16.Tipo_Cliente_ID)
where	(a12.Anio_Mes_NU = 202402 ------------------------------------------------------------------------------>>>>>>>>>>>CAMBIAR PERIODO
 and a13.Producto_T3_CD in ('451')
 and a14.Tipo_Cliente_ID in (3, 4)
 and a11.Estado_Operacion_ID in (4)
 and a11.Estado_Orden_ID in (5)
 and a11.Forma_Adquisicion_SIM_ID in (3, 6, 2)
 and a11.Clasificacion_Operacion_ID in (3, 4))
 and
\$CONDITIONS
group by	1,2,3,4

" --num-mappers 1 --target-dir "hdfs://hdpvelez/user/jpinelli/camp_terminales_casim_1" --input-fields-terminated-by ',';

%jdbc(hive)

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS sandbox_datascientist.jfp_seguimiento_campanias_04;
CREATE TABLE sandbox_datascientist.jfp_seguimiento_campanias_04 as
select * from (
select 
date_format(date_sub(current_date,day(current_date)),'yyyyMMdd') as fecha_medicion, ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------->>>>>>>>> CAMBIAR FECHA
a.mes as mes_base,
a.tipo_cliente_de,
a.ani,
a.caso,
row_number ()  over (partition by a.ani, a.caso order by a.ani ) as rnk,
---cater
case 
when a.caso='cater-apple' and b1.ani is not null then 1 
when a.caso='cater-android' and b1.ani is not null then 1 
when a.caso='cater-apple' and b1.ani is null then 0 
when a.caso='cater-android' and b1.ani is null then 0
else 'N/A' end as fl_campania_cater,

---casim
case 
when a.caso='casim' and b2.ani is not null then 1 
when a.caso='casim' and b2.ani is null then 0 
else 'N/A' end as fl_campania_casim,

---SO
case 
when c1.tac=c2.tac and c2.tac=c3.tac and c1.version_num=c2.version_num and c2.version_num=c3.version_num then 1 else 0 end as fl_validacion_tac,
case 
when a.caso not in ('act-android', 'act-apple') then 'N/A'
when a.caso in ('act-android', 'act-apple')
and (c1.tac=c2.tac and c2.tac=c3.tac and c1.version_num=c2.version_num and c2.version_num=c3.version_num) 
and cast(c1.version_num as float)>cast(a.version_num as float) then 1 
---cierre
when  a.caso in ('act-android') and  x.ani is not null and  cast(a.version_num as float)<cast(x.version_num as float) then 1 
when  a.caso in ('act-apple') and  x.ani is not null and fl_total_so not in ('actualizable', 'Obsoleto') then 1 
when  a.caso in ('act-android', 'act-apple') and x.ani is null then 0
---
else 0
end as fl_campania_so

from sandbox_datascientist.jfp_seguimiento_campanias_01 a
left join sandbox_datascientist.jfp_seguimiento_campanias_cater b1 on b1.ani=a.ani
left join sandbox_datascientist.jfp_seguimiento_campanias_casim b2 on b2.ani=a.ani
left join sandbox_datascientist.jfp_seguimiento_campanias_03 c1 on c1.ani=a.ani and c1.rnk=1
left join sandbox_datascientist.jfp_seguimiento_campanias_03 c2 on c2.ani=a.ani and c2.rnk=2
left join sandbox_datascientist.jfp_seguimiento_campanias_03 c3 on c3.ani=a.ani and c3.rnk=3
--cierre
left join (select * from sandbox.jg_tablero_terminales where tipo_cliente_de in('Individuo','Empresa') and fl_navegador='NAVEGADOR' and mes=date_format(add_months(current_date,-1),'yyyyMM'))x on x.ani=a.ani ----cambiar fecha  MODIF 202209 x 202207 JB 121022
--
)x where rnk=1
;
